Class SimpMessageMappingInfo

  • java.lang.Object

    public class SimpMessageMappingInfo
extends Object
implements MessageCondition<SimpMessageMappingInfo>
    MessageCondition for SImple Messaging Protocols. Encapsulates the following request mapping conditions:
    1. SimpMessageTypeMessageCondition
    2. DestinationPatternsMessageCondition

    4.0
